Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.42,0:00:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Together they fought...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.02,0:00:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,in the spirit of youthful camaraderie.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.86,0:00:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Isato Kaiza...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.69,0:00:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,In the spirit of his own jubilant\Nre-awakening...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.40,0:00:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,he seeks to make amends for\Na wrong he committed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.93,0:00:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He faces his vengeful foe, haunted like\Na criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.57,0:00:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Kash Mizutani...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.70,0:00:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Trapped within the society he so\Ndespised...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.01,0:00:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and which he understood would soon meet\Nits own demise...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.98,0:00:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,he strives to unshackle himself from the\Nburdens of his childhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.18,0:00:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyosuke Shigure...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.82,0:00:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The scent of revenge permeating his\Nbody.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.22,0:00:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Fighting to prove his own worth as a\Nhuman...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.92,0:00:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,setting up the confrontation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.42,0:00:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Deep within his conscience...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.96,0:00:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,he was seeking to wipe out the memory\Nof his own brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.56,0:00:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.60,0:00:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,there is a man who continues\Nto wait in the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.47,0:00:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it that he is waiting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.10,0:00:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it a creation... or is it utter\Ndestruction?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.47,0:00:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The moment is at hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.14,0:00:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The final chapter of this legend...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.34,0:00:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,is about to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.31,0:01:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The Voltage Fighter: Gowcaizer 3
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.32,0:01:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,They haven't learned a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.35,0:01:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Then again... neither have I.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.16,0:01:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Isato...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.46,0:01:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.06,0:01:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ball Boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.32,0:01:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That can only mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.36,0:01:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Shaia!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.20,0:02:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.84,0:02:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get 'em, Karin!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.01,0:02:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.81,0:02:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Shining Cluster! Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.94,0:02:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The ultimate...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.61,0:02:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaen Henpou!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.58,0:02:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's perfection!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.35,0:02:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it! Yet again!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.24,0:02:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to rub you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.21,0:02:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Die, Gowcaizer!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.84,0:02:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Isato Kaiza!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.10,0:03:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of the way, Kash.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.87,0:03:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It is certainly not\Nmy intention to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.10,0:03:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You should know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.50,0:03:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I've recently considered doing volunteer\Nwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.01,0:03:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Well I see that you're going to\Nvolunteer your life this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.48,0:03:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Graviton Knuckle!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.72,0:03:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Beated Needle!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.57,0:03:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,On Bazaragini Harachihataya Souka.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.78,0:03:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.75,0:04:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It is not easy to be laying in wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.59,0:04:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been held in an unchanging state\Nover the past 3 years, Kyosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.76,0:04:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see right through you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.83,0:04:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Anger will reduce your powers by half.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.47,0:04:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you forgotten\Nwhat I've taught you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.10,0:04:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ozaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.34,0:04:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I have one last question for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.24,0:04:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.24,0:04:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you have to harm my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.21,0:04:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it because you needed me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.28,0:04:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it because you needed my power!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.48,0:04:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.72,0:04:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I needed Mia so that I could give you a\Nspecial power.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.79,0:04:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And once you were re-born\Nwith your new power...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.63,0:04:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I needed to increase the strength\Nof that power...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.40,0:04:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And Mia had to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.90,0:04:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It was my intention all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.04,0:04:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.81,0:04:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember, Kyosuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.67,0:04:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Day in and day out...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.68,0:04:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,late into dusk,\NI taught you how to use your powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.05,0:05:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And you responded very well in every\Nway.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.68,0:05:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,A most excellent ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.22,0:05:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.26,0:05:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything seemed to be proceeding just\Nas I wanted it to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.36,0:05:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.23,0:05:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I sensed that I miscalculated\Nsomething.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.13,0:05:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And that was the love that you began to\Nshow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.43,0:05:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps you saw me as a father figure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.84,0:05:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't expect it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.44,0:05:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So in order to break\Nthat relationship...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.48,0:05:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,although premature, I took the life of\NMia.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.38,0:05:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.61,0:05:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It seemed that I'd made another\Nmiscalculation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.68,0:05:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.72,0:05:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That is, the love she had for me was\Ndeeper than I could have imagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.06,0:05:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Even when I sentenced her\Nto her death...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.66,0:05:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,she stepped forward\Nand offered her neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.63,0:05:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What was necessary...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.50,0:05:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,were the anguished cries...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.03,0:05:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyosuke, it was the neck of Mia\Nas she cried for your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.54,0:05:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It weighed heavily on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.57,0:05:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.41,0:06:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You were siblings hungering for love.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.54,0:06:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really a question of disposition,\Nbut it's so sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.31,0:06:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.73,0:06:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't rush it, Kyosuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.80,0:06:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Now is the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.60,0:06:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,that I will reveal the other half\Nof my soul...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.70,0:06:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,that of the providence of god.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.67,0:06:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.43,0:06:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The judgment...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.47,0:07:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.97,0:07:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You had to but in, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.84,0:07:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Just stay out of this, it'll end\Nquickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.48,0:07:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut your mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.81,0:07:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You want this to end in another\Nmeaningless sacrifice!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.99,0:07:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Do what you want then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.92,0:07:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But let me warn you first\Nthat she no longer has a human soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.96,0:07:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Your cheap humanistic approach will land\Nyou in a grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.40,0:07:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think it's the time to be\Nbickering.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.23,0:07:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Or do you think I'm a pushover.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.30,0:07:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.57,0:07:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You afraid?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.44,0:07:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Or are you merely plotting your response\Nto my attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.81,0:07:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Come and get me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.15,0:07:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The Soul Gear! That's suicide!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.28,0:07:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Isato!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.85,0:07:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what you've got in mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.79,0:07:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,but you fool yourself if you think you\Ncan stand up to me without Soul Gear!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.93,0:08:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzu Asahina!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.66,0:08:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,If your goal is to kill me pure and\Nsimple...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.90,0:08:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,then I'm not going to stop you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.61,0:08:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Come!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.69,0:08:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Look. You are human after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.09,0:08:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,When you cause harm to another person...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.16,0:08:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,you will surely be hurting\Nyour own soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.57,0:08:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,However much you want to kill that\Nperson.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.21,0:08:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what happens, I will protect\Nyou.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.15,0:08:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you, Suzu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.85,0:08:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,My dear brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.07,0:09:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.61,0:09:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,My dear brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.82,0:09:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Kash! Kash!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.89,0:09:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey hey, don't be\Ntaking advantage of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.59,0:09:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like being called\Nonly when it's convenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.69,0:09:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on. I'm sorry about before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.60,0:09:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Just try to save her somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.87,0:09:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something weird going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.04,0:09:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.47,0:09:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy of the Caizer is building up\Nwithin her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.08,0:10:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,If it ruptures, that's the end of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.88,0:10:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop kidding around! Do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.85,0:10:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the authority on the Caizer!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.55,0:10:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What authority?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.70,0:10:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Kash.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.00,0:10:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take my Caizer...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.34,0:10:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and align it against hers\Nto neutralize its power.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.87,0:10:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,If it fails, then I suppose we go to\Nheaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.48,0:10:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You go on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.58,0:10:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got other things\Nto take care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.95,0:10:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I won't kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.42,0:10:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.85,0:10:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you, Kash.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.62,0:10:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.23,0:10:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He can run already.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.27,0:10:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,He sure can recover quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.50,0:10:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, just as you wished...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.44,0:11:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I am volunteering to risk my life\Non account of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.47,0:11:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,How did I develop such a\Nself-sacrificing character like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.61,0:11:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I was railing against all that\Nuptight society from my childhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.45,0:11:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen carefully, Kash.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.79,0:11:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you've been born into this\Nfamily...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.16,0:11:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,you will lead a life in which your\Nperformances yield $10,000 per minute...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.43,0:11:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,10 minutes will yield you $100,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.93,0:11:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ignore all distractions and never waver.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.53,0:11:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let anyone take your genius\Naway from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.50,0:11:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You must live your life for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.17,0:11:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Only for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.21,0:11:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, so much for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.16,0:11:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Kyosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.46,0:11:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Penetrate! Kamikabura!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.76,0:11:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire Dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.58,0:12:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Your body breaking apart already?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.15,0:12:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You mere human.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.12,0:12:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,When not in a group, you cannot stand up\Nalone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.42,0:12:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You are foolish indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.69,0:12:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.56,0:12:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. I am not the man you used\Nto know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.60,0:12:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,At least on the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.80,0:12:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I am myself, and you,\Nand your friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.54,0:12:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,A great many people\Nare embodied within me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.98,0:12:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.38,0:12:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.98,0:12:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.02,0:12:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose it's beyond the understanding\Nof a dying man such as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.53,0:13:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,To think that you are the one\Nthey await.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.23,0:13:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Like Pygmalions worshipping the statue\Nthey created...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.20,0:13:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Pathetic humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.01,0:13:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It will be but a flash.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.24,0:13:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Kyosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.61,0:13:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Kubira! Is that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.11,0:13:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You can reprimand me later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.52,0:13:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.30,0:13:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Kubira!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.34,0:13:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me, Kubira.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.38,0:13:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.83,0:14:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Kubira!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.03,0:14:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Kubira!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.07,0:14:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations on your victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.71,0:14:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.44,0:14:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Kubira.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.75,0:14:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always considered this to be my\Nfinal duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.98,0:14:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,In order for you to carry out\Nthat duty...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.62,0:14:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I would have had to return to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.02,0:14:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But I am now all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.29,0:14:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Kyosuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.50,0:14:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Please do not fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.13,0:14:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I will always be near you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.07,0:14:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.67,0:14:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You are no longer alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.48,0:15:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Kubira.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.79,0:15:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Kubira!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.96,0:15:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.36,0:15:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaiza?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.13,0:15:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyosuke! Behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.84,0:15:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.95,0:15:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,This can't be what Kash was talking\Nabout!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.56,0:15:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This is JG02. There is a mysterious\Nenergy emitting from...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.73,0:15:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.24,0:15:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you do with Kyosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.14,0:16:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the will of all creation...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.64,0:16:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Omni Exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.78,0:16:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Omni Exist!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.38,0:16:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The embodiment of all thought existing\Nin nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.65,0:16:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I have absorbed within me all of the\Ndesires of humankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.59,0:16:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That is why I came into being.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.53,0:16:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.76,0:16:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I have until now only existed as\Nthought.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.80,0:16:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But Shizuru Ozaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.37,0:16:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,His desires had reached the level\Nof my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.34,0:16:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And through him...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.35,0:16:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I was first able to begin to carry out\Nmy destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.12,0:16:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You humans are despised...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.22,0:16:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,by all of existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.36,0:16:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Bound by the rules you created...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.53,0:16:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,an insane humanity bent on destroying\Neverything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.30,0:17:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The recklessness of disposing into outer\Nspace that which you cannot process...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.37,0:17:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The people who live on a planet bathed\Nin ultraviolet rays...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.11,0:17:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,that reach every corner of the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.28,0:17:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That is what you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.58,0:17:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The destruction of earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.71,0:17:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It is the desire of all humankind, and I\Nam the one who will carry it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.15,0:17:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.22,0:17:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.72,0:17:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.93,0:17:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that you've feared the future\Nat least at one time in your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.33,0:17:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The good things and the bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.40,0:17:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It is surely frightening to look at the\Nfuture no matter what your position.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.81,0:17:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,A world that does not progress...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.51,0:17:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That is something that's certain to\Nbring relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.61,0:17:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the one you refer to as Kyosuke\Ndesires this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.52,0:17:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Even you wish it deep in your\Nsubconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.12,0:17:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The end of everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.49,0:18:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong! I'm not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.89,0:18:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.00,0:18:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But eventually, my powers will destroy\Nthe earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.10,0:18:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Then all will end.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.01,0:18:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to let you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.64,0:18:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you will have to try and stop me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.08,0:18:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You can only succeed if either\Nyour energy exceeds mine...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.92,0:18:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,or if all of existence can be\Npersuaded...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.52,0:18:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and cause me to completely loose\Nmy will.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.09,0:18:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Both seem preposterous at this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.36,0:18:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds interesting...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.16,0:18:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Well I'm not much\Nof a pursuasive talker...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.36,0:18:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,but to exceed your power is something\NI can give a shot at.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.34,0:18:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Caizer Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.62,0:19:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Caizer Strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.60,0:19:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Burny Samona!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.15,0:19:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Shaia.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.32,0:19:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope Isato and them are gonna be all\Nright.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.95,0:19:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.09,0:19:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,There're not going to loose that easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.89,0:19:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.99,0:19:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not gonna loose.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.83,0:19:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.71,0:19:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit. I can't let it end like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.54,0:20:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No way, Isato! It's not in your nature\Nto give up like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.58,0:20:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Isato!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.35,0:20:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.19,0:20:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.37,0:20:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Kash!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.53,0:20:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Knowing the kind of guy you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.47,0:20:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured you'd be playing up\Nthat high drama yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.24,0:20:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.94,0:20:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what did you do with the girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.08,0:20:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I delivered the princess to\Nher castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.12,0:20:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyper Voltage...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.55,0:20:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform Hellstinger!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.92,0:20:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh! And what did you come here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.03,0:20:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.53,0:20:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't you heard?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.46,0:20:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to round up the finale.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.80,0:20:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Knowing you, this might never\Ncome to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.74,0:21:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need any of that at a time like\Nthis.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.57,0:21:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,As I suspected, to band together...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.04,0:21:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,is a human tendency.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.28,0:21:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose that can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.38,0:21:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Here she comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.62,0:21:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I'll set up a decoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.82,0:21:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You go straight for the attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.32,0:21:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.36,0:21:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Lineck Singer!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.46,0:21:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Now's your chance, Isato!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.57,0:21:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Isato!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.04,0:21:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You're doing very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.31,0:21:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You have my praise.\NI will now give you your reward!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.86,0:21:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sleepy, Kyosuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.43,0:22:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.83,0:22:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sleepy, dear brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.80,0:22:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Very sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.54,0:22:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No Kyosuke. You mustn't sleep yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.84,0:22:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,My sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.51,0:22:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It is now that we need your strength the\Nmost.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.11,0:22:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Kubira is here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.72,0:22:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot see anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.72,0:22:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides... I'm no longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.36,0:22:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Take my hand, Kyosuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.03,0:22:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I will show you the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.86,0:22:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It is my final wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.70,0:22:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.04,0:22:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.01,0:22:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Quite amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.18,0:22:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,To think that the human will can be so\Nsublime...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.69,0:22:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't seen nothing yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.26,0:23:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We can be foolish and we often fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.69,0:23:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We can also think evil thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.03,0:23:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But on the other hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.13,0:23:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,only humans will sacrifice their lives\Nto help save those close to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.84,0:23:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh! Well I'm just the kind of fool\Nthat'll fall for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.51,0:23:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Using your power to save everyone isn't\Nsomething that hasn't crossed my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.15,0:23:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show you what it's all about...!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.92,0:23:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The unlimited possibilities of human\Nbeings!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.05,0:23:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got quite an attitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.62,0:23:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It is time that I show you the eternal\Nagony of nothingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.69,0:23:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This doesn't look good...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.69,0:23:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,These forces are like no other we've\Nfelt yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.66,0:23:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Isato!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.13,0:23:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Foolish one...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.24,0:23:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha...!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.91,0:23:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on!?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.92,0:24:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.09,0:24:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you, my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.19,0:24:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.83,0:24:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,but I am human after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.23,0:24:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Now's the time. Come Kaiza!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.47,0:24:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But... But Kyosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.20,0:24:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.17,0:24:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Come!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.04,0:24:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Kash!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.71,0:24:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.72,0:24:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.59,0:24:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I've paid my debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.62,0:24:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.04,0:25:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Here me well, humankind...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.58,0:25:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I have not given up.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.42,0:25:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And I have not died.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.85,0:25:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a momentary lapse of direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.13,0:25:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I will return at anytime that you\Ndesire.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.13,0:25:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.94,0:25:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Isato...!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.78,0:26:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.92,0:26:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Good to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.53,0:26:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.16,0:27:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I did not want to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.90,0:27:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to bring you back.